data.title: Comparative Analysis of Genome Diversity in Bullmastiff Dogs
data.meta_description: Management and preservation of genomic diversity in dog breeds is a major objective for maintaining health. The present study was undertaken to characterise genomic diversity in Bullmastiff dogs using both genealogical and molecular analysis. Genealogical analysis of diversity was conducted using a …
